statements.sql:
select *, (
6371 * acos(
cos(radians(41.3281482)) * cos(radians(latitude)) *
cos(radians(longitude) - radians(19.8184435)) +
sin(radians(41.3281482)) * sin(radians(latitude))
)
) AS distance from `hotels` having `distance` <= 10 order by `distance` asc limit 11 offset 0
